item.title: You Won't Believe What Happens When You Scan Roll Up The Rim To Win!
item.description: Introduction to Roll Up The Rim To Win Roll Up The Rim To Win is a popular Canadian promotion by Tim Hortons. It is a game that gives customers a chance to win prizes or discounts when they purchase a participating product and scan the Roll Up The Rim To Win tab. Overview of the Process The process of participating in Roll Up The Rim To Win is simple. Customers must first purchase a participating product from Tim Hortons.

item.title: Unlock the Secrets to Roll Up the Rim to Win and Get Your Chance to Win Big!
item.description: Introduction Every year, Canadians look forward to the annual Roll Up the Rim to Win promotion from Tim Hortons. This exciting game gives customers the chance to win amazing prizes, from free coffee to cars and cash! But to have the best chance of winning, it’s important to understand the rules and regulations of the game. In this blog post, we’ll break down the basics of Roll Up the Rim to Win and provide tips on how to maximize your chances of winning.
